longBusinessSummary: Intouch Insight Ltd. develops managed mobile software applications and software-as-a-service platforms, and delivers services for private businesses, governments, and regulators in Canada, the United States, and internationally. The company's software platforms include IntouchCapture, IntouchCheck, IntouchSurvey, and LiaCX that facilitate the development of data collection programs comprising event lead capture, customer satisfaction surveys, and mobile forms, checklist, and audits. It also develops customer experience management software for retailers, restaurants, and hotels; survey software; mobile forms automation software; and event marketing automation software, as well as offers data collection services, including mystery shopping, third party audit, and customer experience measurement programs. The company was formerly known as In-Touch Survey Systems Ltd. and changed its name to Intouch Insight Ltd. in July 2016. Intouch Insight Ltd. was founded in 1992 and is based in Ottawa, Canada.
